Don't miss: Novavax vaccine shows 89 per cent efficacy in UK trials

The #Novavax #Covid19 efficacy showed in phase three of a clinical trial conducted in the UK. The UK has ordered 60 million doses of the #vaccine, writes @Hannah_Godfrey  https://t.co/t8oSH3tSrA #Covidvaccine https://t.co/L3HZvEbWrr
